Paper: hep-th/0202040

Date: 2002-02-06

Title: Anomalies in Noncommutative Dipole Field Theories

Authors: D.H.Correa, G.S.Lozano, E.F.Moreno, F.A.Schaposnik

Comments: 11pages, latex file. Comments added

Journal-ref: JHEP 0202 (2002) 031

We study chiral symmetries of fermionic non commutative dipole theories. Byusing Fujikawa's approach we obtain explicit expressions of the anomalies forDirac and chiral fermions in 2 and 4 dimensions.